						<summary>

						<p>Slab with the image of Āñjanēya set up under the pipal tree near the tank.</p>						

						<p>The date is expressed by the chronogram <hi rend="bold">vasu-vārāśi-guṇa-indu</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1348, Parābhava, Kārttīka śu. 13,</hi> corresponding to 1426 A.D., October 28, Monday.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a tank by Hamsanāyaka, son of Purushōttama and Chennamāmba.</p>						

						</summary>
